text: Joban Uddin Ahmad is a Bangladesh Jamaat-e-Islami politician and the former Member of Parliament of the constituency Nilphamari-3. ==Career== Ahmed was elected to parliament from Nilphamari-3 as a Bangladesh Jamaat-e-Islami candidate in 1986. ==References== Category:Bangladesh Jamaat-e-Islami politicians Category:Politicians from Rangpur Division Category:Living people
title: Joban Uddin Ahmad
